14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. There is hereby appropriated to the Weigh Station
16 Improvement Revolving Fund, created pursuant to Section 1167 of
17 Title 47 of the Oklahoma Statutes, from any monies not otherwise
18 appropriated from the General Revenue Fund of the State Treasury for
19 the fiscal year ending June 30, 2023, the sum of Nine Million
20 Dollars ($9,000,000.00) or so much thereof as may be necessary to
21 perform the duties imposed upon the Department of Transportation by
22 law.
23 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective July 1, 2025.
